Package com.steelypip.powerups.jinxml.stdrender

Class ThemeableWriter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.steelypip.powerups.jinxml.stdrender.ThemeableWriter<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ElementWriter
    public class ThemeableWriter<T>
extends Object
    Prints out an object to a PrintWriter. It can be a simple-all-on-one-line or an elaborate pretty-printer depending on the Indenter, and look like XML or JSON depending on the Theme that is supplied.
